title: Amiga music: JosSs - Greased Machine (A1200🎧Dolbyfied)
description:
"Greased Machine" (2022) by JosSs (José Manuel Pérez Paredes). Art "Reminiscent of Dante's Underworld" by Koyot1222/Matys, 6th at Revision 2022. Read more about the art below...

The original art features non-black background (or more like foreground :). For this video i had the audacity to exchange the non-black color to pure black color. You can see the art in its original form here:
https://www.artstation.com/artwork/mzlJNd
